      7  10000 ????						; UP 1 WAY (Atari 2600, 4K)
      8  10000 ????						;
      9  10000 ????						; This file is intentionally documented and organized in readable sections.
     10  10000 ????						; The code currently implements:
     11  10000 ????						; - stable frame structure (VSYNC / VBLANK / kernel / overscan)
     12  10000 ????						; - lane-based player movement (jump up, fall on gap)
     13  10000 ????						; - scrolling gap model
     14  10000 ????						; - placeholder cone/skull entities with collision hooks
     15  10000 ????						; - HUD placeholder strip at top of screen
     16  10000 ????						;
     17  10000 ????						; The goal is a clean, extensible baseline that we can iterate on.
     18  10000 ????						; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
     19  10000 ????
     20  10000 ????						; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
     21  10000 ????						; Constants
     22  10000 ????						; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
